2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 e6 6. Be2 Be7 7. O-O O-O 8. f4 Nc6 9.
Be3 a6 10. a4 Qc7 {Scheveningen Sicilian tabiya.} 11. Kh1 (11. Bf3)) 1... Nf6
2. Nc3 e5 3. Nf3 Nc6 4. d3 {A relatively rare move order, aiming to avoid the
