With the knight on d8 this swap is more unpleasant.} cxd6 23. Nc3 {[%cal Rc3d5]
} d5 (23... Rc8 24. Nd5 Rxc1 25. Rxc1 Nc6 26. g5 {()} Kf8 27. e3 $16) 24. Na4
Rb8 25. e3 {[%cal Gc1c8]} f6 {[#]} (25... Ne6 26. Nc5 Nxc5 27. Rxc5 $14) 26. f4
$16 (26. Rc2 Ne6 27. Rec1 d4 $132) 26... g6 (26... exf4 27. exf4 Nc6 28. Nc5
$36) (26... Nc6 $5 27. Nc5 Rd6 28. f5 d4 29. e4 Nd8 {[%cal Yb8c8,Yd6c6] gives
Black chances to neutralise the pull.}) 27. Rc2 Ne6 (27... Nc6 28. Nc5 Rd6 29.
Rec1 (29. Rf2 exf4 30. exf4 (30. Rxf4 Kg7) 30... Nd4 31. Re7 b6 32. Rd7 Rd8 33.
