gxf5 29. gxf5 Ng7 30. Rf1 d4 $6 {Frees f4 for Black's knight, but now the Pf5
is protected and White can centralise his K.} (30... Kh8 $5 $14 {[%cal Yb8g8]
would force it to the h-file.}) 31. e4 $1 Nh5 (31... b5 32. Nc5 Rc7 33. Kf3 $36
) 32. Nb6 Rg7+ (32... Nf4+ 33. Kf3 Rf7 (33... Rg7 {-32...Rg7}) 34. Rg1+ Kf8 35.
