again fast enough.}) 46... Re1+ $2 {Costs Black a tempo and decides the game.}
(46... Ra1 $2 47. Rb6 Rxa3 48. Rxf6+ Kg7 49. Re6 $18 (49. Rb6 $5 $18)) (46...
Rh1 $1 47. Kd5 Rxh4 48. Rb6 Kg5 49. Rxa6 Rh3 {with a likely draw, e.g.} 50. Kc4
Rh1 51. b5 Rc1+ 52. Kd5 Rb1 53. a4 (53. Kc4 Rc1+ $5) 53... h5 54. b6 h4 55. a5
h3 56. Ra8 Kf4 57. Rh8 Kg3 58. Kc5 Rc1+ 59. Kb5 Rb1+) 47. Kd5 e4 48. Re7 $1 $18
{Navara probably overlooked this blow.} (48. Kxd4 $2 exd3 49. Kxd3 Ra1 50. Ke4
Rxa3 51. Rb6 Rh3 52. Rxf6+ Kg7) 48... Ra1 {Other moves don't help either:} (
48... e3 49. Kxd4 e2 50. Kd5 Kh5 (50... a5 51. bxa5 Rf1 52. Rxe2 Rxf5+ 53. Ke6
Rxa5 54. d4 $18) 51. Re4 Ra1 (51... Rd1 52. Rxe2 Rxd3+ 53. Ke6 $18) 52. Rxe2
Rxa3 53. d4 $18 {[%cal Rd5e6]}) (48... Re3 49. Rxe4 Rf3 (49... Rxd3 50. Rxd4
Rxa3 51. Ke6 $18) 50. a4 $5 Rxf5+ 51. Kc6 $18 {[%cal Rb4b8]}) (48... Rf1 49.
Rxe4 Rxf5+ 50. Kc6 $1 $18 {[%cal Ya3a4,Yc6b6]}) 49. Rxe4 Rxa3 50. Rxd4 Kh5 51.
Ke6 a5 52. bxa5 Rxa5 53. Kxf6 h6 54. Rd7 Ra4 (54... Kxh4 55. Kg6 {[%cal Rf5f8]}
) 55. Ke7 Rd4 56. f6 {[%csl Gf6] Disarms the stalemate and promotes his o^.}
1-0

[Event "?"]
[Site "?"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
