ready to double the rooks on the f-file.} 18. exf5 Rxf5 19. Ne3 Rf7 20. Nd5
Rbf8 21. Re1 Nc6 $1 $15 {[%cal Gc6e5] The knight is heading to e5 from where
it will control all the important light squares. Black's position has to be
preferred.} 0-1

