contact often allows Black to swing his queen to the kingside. The game
continued} 10. cxd5 Qxd5 11. d3 Qh5 12. Ne3 Bh3 {[%csl Re3,Rg2][%cal Gc6e5,
Ge5g4] After this move, Black is already slightly better. Ideally, after
exchanging the light-squared bishops, Black will exchange a pair of knights as
well. This idea can be executed by means of the manoeuvre...Nc6-e5-g4.} 0-1

