{[#]} 12... Na5 $1 {After ...a7-a5-a4, putting pressure on c4 is Black's most
logical idea.} 13. b4 {Aronian is practicaly forced to go for this undesirable
move which opens the a-file.} ({After} 13. Nd1 Be6 14. Ne3 {Black can proceed
with the thematic} c6 $1 15. O-O d5 {when after} 16. exd5 cxd5 17. cxd5 Nxd5
18. Nxd5 Qxd5 $15 {Black is already better.}) 13... axb3 14. axb3 Nc6 15. Rb1
Be6 16. Nd1 Ne7 $1 {[%cal Gc7c6,Gd6d5] Another precise move. Black is
preparing ...c7-c6 followed by ...d6-d5. In this way, Caruana managed to solve
all the problems.} 0-1

