{In this game, we will analyze the move 11...Bg4, which leads to exciting
complications} 11. h3 {I believe that this move is not the most accurate
because then Black gets a tempo for Qd7} (11. Rc1 Qd7 12. e3 Ne7 (12... Qf5 13.
Nd5 Qh5 14. Nxf6+ gxf6 15. h3 Bxh3 16. Bxh3 Qxh3 17. Nh4 (17. c5 $1 $14 {
