17... b5 $1 {was even stronger}) 18. exf5 Bxf5 19. bxc5 dxc5 {The position is
about equal, but Black manages to win it after many complications} 20. e3 Rad8
21. exd4 cxd4 22. Rfe1 Kh7 23. Bd5 d3 24. f4 Rfe8 25. g4 Bg6 26. f5 Bf7 27.
Qxd3 Bxd5 28. cxd5 Bb8+ 29. Kg2 Qd6 30. f6+ Kg8 31. Rxe8+ Rxe8 32. Qf3 Qh2+ 33.
Kf1 gxf6 34. Bd4 Be5 35. Be3 Bg3 36. Bg1 Qxh3+ 37. Qg2 Qxg4 38. d6 Qf4+ 39. Bf2
Qxc1+ 0-1

