111,79,82,98,107,104,90,95,265,225,251,341,348,346,350,268,256,250,518,604,737,
735,1207,1314]} 1. c4 f5 2. g3 Nf6 3. Bg2 g6 4. Nc3 Bg7 5. d3 d6 6. Rb1 a5 7.
a3 O-O 8. b4 axb4 9. axb4 e5 10. Nf3 Nc6 11. b5 Ne7 12. O-O h6 13. Bb2 Be6 14.
Ra1 Rb8 15. Ra7 Nc8 (15... g5 16. Nd2 Qc8 17. Qb3 (17. Qa1 $5) 17... Kh8 18.
Nd5 (18. Qa3 $1 {[%cal Gf1c1] followed by Rc1}) 18... Neg8 19. Qa3 f4 20. d4
$14 {Bravo Lutz,S (2158)-Kuhn,U (2019) Offenbach 2005 (0-1, 47) After reaching
maximum of activity, White breaks the centre.}) 16. Ra5 g5 17. Qa1 (17. Qb3 {
is also possible.}) 17... Nb6 (17... Nd7 18. Nd2 Nc5 19. Nd5 c6 20. Nb4 $16)
18. Nd2 f4 19. Ra7 Qc8 20. Rc1 {A subtle move, preparing Nd5 and, in some
cases, c4-c5.} Nbd7 21. Nd5 (21. Nce4 Nxe4 (21... Kh8 22. c5 d5 23. Nxf6 Bxf6
24. c6) 22. Nxe4 Qd8 23. Bc3 $5 {The start of a massive regrouping, aimed at
increasing the control over the a-file.} (23. c5 d5) 23... Rf7 (23... g4 24.
gxf4 Rxf4 25. Bd2 Rf7 26. Be3) 24. Rc2 g4 25. Rca2 f3 26. Bf1 Nb6 27. Bd2 $14 {
followed by Be3.}) 21... Qd8 (21... Nxd5 $5 {is not appealing, but may offer
better chances to stay in the game.} 22. cxd5 Bf5 23. Nc4 Qd8 (23... Nc5 24. b6
Nb3 25. Nxd6 Qd7 26. Rxc7 Qxd6 27. Rxg7+ Kxg7 28. Bxe5+ $18) 24. Na5 Qc8 (24...
Nc5 25. Rxc5 dxc5 26. Nxb7 $16) 25. Qa2 Nb6 26. Ba3 Ra8 27. Rxa8 Qxa8 28. Bb4
Rf7 {White has strong pressure, but he still must generate a concrete plan.})
22. Nxf6+ Qxf6 23. Rf1 $1 (23. Ne4 {[%csl Gb7] would release the pressure on
b7.}) 23... Bg4 (23... Nc5 24. Ba3 Qe7 $5 (24... Qf7 25. Bxc5 dxc5 26. Bxb7 e4
27. Qd1 exd3 28. exd3) 25. Bxc5 dxc5 26. Be4 (26. Rxb7 Rxb7 27. Bxb7 e4 28. Qe1
e3 {With the queen on f7, this does not work.}) 26... Kh8 (26... b6 27. Qa6)
27. b6 cxb6 (27... c6 28. Qa5 $16) 28. Qb2 Qf7 29. f3 $16) 24. Qd1 (24. Bd5+
Kh8 25. Ne4 Qg6 26. f3 Bh3 27. Bxb7 Bxf1 28. Qxf1 $16) 24... c6 25. Ba3 $18 Nc5
26. bxc6 bxc6 27. Bxc6 $18 Bh3 28. Bg2 Bxg2 29. Kxg2 g4 30. f3 gxf3+ 31. Rxf3
Qd8 32. Bxc5 dxc5 33. Ne4 Qb6 34. Qa4 Rbd8 35. Qa5 Qg6 36. Qxc5 Rb8 37. Qd5+
Kh8 38. c5 fxg3 39. Rxg3 Qf5 40. Rgxg7 Qf1+ 41. Kg3 Qf4+ 42. Kh3 Qf5+ 43. Rg4
h5 44. Qd7 hxg4+ 45. Kh4 Qg6 46. Qd6 Qxd6 47. cxd6 Rbd8 48. Kg5 Rf4 49. Nf6
Rxf6 50. Kxf6 Rxd6+ 51. Kg5 e4 52. dxe4 Rd2 53. e5 Kg8 54. Kg6 Kf8 55. Kf6 1-0

